{"tid":164421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個大仆街 求屌醒","createTime":"2017-03-20T15:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T04:31:23.000Z","uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4307d88e86d50ff527008deb47bb85915f2a4e0a","tid":164421,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次有咩唔想講就呃女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家出嚟做野 職業唔同 所以其實都唔識大家啲同事<br />\n女朋友好有異性緣 但都同異性保持距離<br />\n佢真係好好 我都好想好好珍惜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但奈何我係一個大仆街<br />\n成日有好少事都呃佢 每次都比佢發現到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實我都唔想呃佢 <br />\n但係我真係好衝動 有啲唔想講嘅野就是但鳩噏hea撚咗佢就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呃完佢會好內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應承佢無下次 自己都好想改<br />\n但下一次又呃過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為咁嘈過好多次 分過好多次手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但女朋友都好好 選擇原諒我<br />\n唔知佢仲忍到幾多次 我都唔想佢再承受<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補充一點 真係好少事都呃 唔係偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我點樣先可以改 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  第一次對個女仔咁認真 咁愛一個人 想同佢有將來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔想因為自己咁而失去咗個好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同我一齊之前係處 我唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢比咗隻豬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （20幾歲）之前有拍過拖 拍咗幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢真係好愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原本拒絕婚前性行爲 但因為我⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我好想比到將來佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係事事將我擺第一 為咗陪我犧牲咗好多陪朋友嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次帶男朋友返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時肯AA 見我無錢仲會塞錢比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁好嘅女仔去邊搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕撚哂種 唔似啲港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且又靚又叻女有長腿有波路<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又多人追 點解要揀我呢個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心真意想改<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想失去佢<br />\n琴日又呃撚咗佢 宜家好撚大鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d023516deeb1699d37645a17508512e995ba4c5b","tid":164421,"uid":44175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51d0e62a62b604ea3eef4a0093a9b6d255f6038","tid":164421,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日因為有個隔離team女同事搵我吹咗兩句水 我女朋友問我做乜online咁耐都唔覆佢 <br />\n呃撚咗佢話係同男同事傾公事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c194cfdbe8eea295c49bd1b172f58f5316fdf1d","tid":164421,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:08:48.000Z","msg":"你女友鍾意你d乜"},{"pid":"21289fa80a7ba01357421d8134834419b6d7aab2","tid":164421,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你女友鍾意你d乜</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94adbb3ce1ba113a3a4e2d0873ddd0b1929799f3","tid":164421,"uid":12879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:16:49.000Z","msg":"將心比己啦 如果佢都喺咁對你 你會點<br />\n咁小事都要講大話 總有一日佢都喺會知真相 你依家嗰情況根本無改善到 結果都喺會犯重複嘅錯 你咁樣唔改真喺幾好嘅女仔都會走啦"},{"pid":"4af2ebc0cd186e0fcc12679772e0af75d957a068","tid":164421,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日因為有個隔離team女同事搵我吹咗兩句水 我女朋友問我做乜online咁耐都唔覆佢 <br />\n呃撚咗佢話係同男同事傾公事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先 呢啲細大話就算鳩數<br />\n當粉筆字算 咁你個心就定啲啦<br />\n最憎啲男人把口又講到點愛點愛又後悔<br />\n做又唔嗲唔吊成個女人咁<br />\n做出黎比人睇好過叫春啦垃圾"},{"pid":"00c9f673fb98d514ba115e892f48c5452f204f61","tid":164421,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將心比己啦 如果佢都喺咁對你 你會點<br />\n咁小事都要講大話 總有一日佢都喺會知真相 你依家嗰情況根本無改善到 結果都喺會犯重複嘅錯 你咁樣唔改真喺幾好嘅女仔都會走啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<br />\n樓主似係利用緊條女既同情心同忍耐力 <br />\n終有一日佢會頂唔順離你而去<br />\n一次原諒你叫情有可原，兩三次十幾次就叫不可原諒，人既忍耐力去到一個點就真係點都會爆，唔理佢之前係有幾愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好好諗下當佢有一日頂你唔順<br />\n唔再原諒你飛左你<br />\n開始溝其他仔，同其他仔出街<br />\n將對你既好同關懷對左第二條仔<br />\n同第二條仔攬錫扑野瘋狂中出<br />\n咁你可能先會知後悔係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a964b5d19ff53c0a7538b0977bed68764788a83c","tid":164421,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將心比己啦 如果佢都喺咁對你 你會點<br />\n咁小事都要講大話 總有一日佢都喺會知真相 你依家嗰情況根本無改善到 結果都喺會犯重複嘅錯 你咁樣唔改真喺幾好嘅女仔都會走啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收到啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會改嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66d77aa5f03a75e223e873052ae75cb5aa2a9a1","tid":164421,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日因為有個隔離team女同事搵我吹咗兩句水 我女朋友問我做乜online咁耐都唔覆佢 <br />\n呃撚咗佢話係同男同事傾公事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先 呢啲細大話就算鳩數<br />\n當粉筆字算 咁你個心就定啲啦<br />\n最憎啲男人把口又講到點愛點愛又後悔<br />\n做又唔嗲唔吊成個女人咁<br />\n做出黎比人睇好過叫春啦垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錯，講得好啱"},{"pid":"18c04575c97f6b026d0d92f52651d13aab667f26","tid":164421,"uid":299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>將心比己啦 如果佢都喺咁對你 你會點<br />\n咁小事都要講大話 總有一日佢都喺會知真相 你依家嗰情況根本無改善到 結果都喺會犯重複嘅錯 你咁樣唔改真喺幾好嘅女仔都會走啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收到啦巴打<img src=\"